        <obo:IAO_0000115>An acute inflammatory response to an antigenic stimulus. An acute inflammatory response occurs within a matter of minutes or hours, and either resolves within a few days or becomes a chronic inflammatory response.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <oboInOwl:hasOBONamespace>biological_process</oboInOwl:hasOBONamespace>
