        <obo:UBPROP_0000007>mandibular</obo:UBPROP_0000007>
        <obo:UBPROP_0000012>Note in ZFA &apos;mandible&apos; is a syn for the ventral mandibular arch, which is a portion of the 1st pharyngeal arch; however the term &apos;mandibular symphysis&apos; refers to the dentary</obo:UBPROP_0000012>
        <obo:UBPROP_0000013>&apos;mandible&apos; also refers to either the upper OR lower part of the beak in birds</obo:UBPROP_0000013>
